_sText:
Thank you for downloading gg_doppler.

This is the first map that I've done with experimentations in bump mapping. The screenshots should speak for themselves. So far so good, I hope you enjoy it.

Perfect for short range weapons, long range weapons, knifing and hegrenades.

This map also has buy-zones for anyone who wishes to have this on any non-gungame server.

All textures created/shopped by myself.

If you'd like to play this map on our gg server, please join us at:

208.146.44.32:27015

or visit us on the fourms:

http://seattle-ducksoup.com/index.php

Thank you!

--Manqueef/Emeriastone
